Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.001\fs75\c&H0521D2&\3c&HEAE9C3&\4c&H38B04E&\bord5\shad8\pos(760,870)\fad(900,0)}Here Comes the High Collar Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,20,,Did you hear about it?{Have you heard the gossip already?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:17.96,Default,,0,0,20,,And have you seen it?{And have you made sure yourself with those eyes?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,20,,Those two shockingly beautiful eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:27.52,Default,,0,0,20,,Overflowing with startling romance{A shockingly overflowing romance}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.73,Default,,0,0,20,,All-consuming{The hottest topic now}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,20,,Inescapable{It's all about this}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:36.32,Default,,0,0,20,,With a Taishō Era charming lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.08,0:00:49.46,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:53.84,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:58.09,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:02.47,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:06.81,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that they've ascertained \Nthat Shinobu's is Japan's #1 bridegroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,even Benio's father shed some tears of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.55,0:01:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, also brimming with joy, \Ninvited her classmates to the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,However, fate loves irony, \Nas Shinobu is about to be transferred,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.70,0:01:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,rendering a seemingly heavenly situation hellish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt Col Innen clearly pulled the strings \Nthat led to this devilish intervention in fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But the orders are not up for debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Still unaware of all of this, \NBenio's classmates arrive to celebrate...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the last straw for our High Collar Lady, \Nso she prepares to storm the garrison herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Bloodshed seems inevitable today. {/somewhere, the blood is going to rain}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:02:02.53,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(00,0)\b1\blur0.6\bord1\3c&HDDDADB&\c&HB5762F&\move(724,100,724,158,0,200)\4c&HFFFFFF&}Episode 24 \N {\fs100.001} I Can't Stand Martinets!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait, Lady Benio. \NDon't be so hasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right. \NStirring things up will only make matters worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not the kind of people you can reason with!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialog is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.07,0:02:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ranmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is it true that you're storming \Nthe army headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it look like I'm doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.71,0:02:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my only allies here, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu's deployment to Kyushu \Nis part of one big conspiracy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't possibly let this slide!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who gets in my way, \Nbe it the Imperial Army or whoever else...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,will be chopped in half just like this tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are your worries, \Nriverside willow? {https://blog.goo.ne.jp/np4626/e/adfc462950205a8dee498b2b37f58f6c - this song, either keep this kind of adaptation or put another popular english song}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with the belligerent outfit, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect timing. \NUshigorou, I need a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy to follow my boss through fire and water\Nand 'til the end of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:03:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where are we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Imperial Army, first division.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! W-What did you just say, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're mounting an attack \Non the 1st Division headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you even call yourself a man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's because I'm a man that I\Nknow exactly why this is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boss, I don't know all the details,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but I know damn well\Nthat you don't wanna antagonize the Imperial Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done. \NOur Boss-Henchman alliance is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenmaru, Chimaru, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Assaulting them on your own \Nis biting off more than you can chew!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's no stopping her now! \NI gotta do something 'bout it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, stopping Benio should be done \Nwith words, not spears!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:04:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not planning to stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, I'll go back her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't "not again" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not hard to understand how Benio feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.52,0:05:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stand by Benio's side, \Ncome hell or high water! {/through thick and thin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu is my grandson, which makes his bride Benio \Nmy cherished granddaughter too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who gets in the way \Nwill meet my spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way!\NThis is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, the wedding ceremony \Nis just around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait for the day to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny! Nanny, t-t-this is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Whenever you come here, it doesn't bode well, so I don't want to listen to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A father and his daughter are about to cross swords! {/about to cross swords}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Cross swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Ushi, what is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Gladly. If memory serves me, \NLord Hanamura is in 1st Division, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:07:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.\NWhat about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why I'm saying \Nthat they're about to cross swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Boss went to assault \Ntheir headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the wedding ceremony \Nis still a long way off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Lady Kichiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! This is real bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss went... \N1st Division...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi, please explain things calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:08:00.61,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HD4D5CE&\blur2\3c&HC0A371&\fs100\frz345.3\pos(640.38,212.44)}Milk bar
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The wife sympathizes with her husband, \Nwhile the husband yearns for his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Both parties come to each other's rescue. \NThat's what being a couple means.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood? Then keep it in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to barge in, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This disgusting man again!\NI can't stand him, I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Tamaki, I was looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Ushigorou?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear me out! Boss is... \NBoss is in a pickle big time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura is up to something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, call from the 1st Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Major Hanamura here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a pleasure to hear from Benio's father.\NThe Ijuuins are listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're just who I needed, Countess.\NI wanted to make sure Benio didn't do anything silly. {/make a mistake}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She might just be {\i1}about{\i0} to do something silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-Wha-Wh-What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,For this reason, I wanted Shinobu to intervene,\Nas he is the only one who can stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, the lieutenant is not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where is he, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Presently, he left for Toyamagahara with his unit \Nto conduct his last drill as part of the 1st Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear me! And you can't summon him back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please understand, \Nthe Imperial Army waits for no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's just a military exercise, \Nthe expectations are set as high as in a real battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,0:09:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,One should be prepared \Nto be sent into battle any moment. {no idea what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going! No retreat! Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So cruel, sending Shinobu to Kyushu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sincerely believe that your marriage \Nwill be the one that stands the test of time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't just let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I will... I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait, Innen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll regret bullying my dear Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't get away with it!{all lines from 171 to 177 are partly personalised to adapt them to the context as I can't hear them clearly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:55.16,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Yes, we'll deal with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sounds good. \NMission: aid Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:11:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll show them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone!\NThat's the spirit of classmate camaraderie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on a spell... Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A man's left behind by his party.\NLet's admit him to our circle now! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Goldfish Ushigorou is the manliest man alive!\NSticks and stones may break my bones, you hear? {lit: bring on the arrows and cannons}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Our hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing you up close, \NI'm having second thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask where the five of you \Nare going all together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to assault the 1st Division \Nheadquarters, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, please let this slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.07,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, we're begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:12:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Times like these are when having a good leader is crucial.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm prepared to take that role upon myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're coming with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The tyranny of the military must be stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The true victims of any war are always women! {/made to cry}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We must protest against militarism!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:15.03,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(600,700)\c&H1E100D&\3c&HE6E8E2&}Eternal devotion to motherland{a varation on 七生報国 (unfailing devotion to one's country; serving one's country for seven lives​) with 国 being "國: Out-dated kanji or kanji usage."}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:30.05,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1E100D&\3c&HE6E8E2&\fade(1500,0)}Eternal devotion to motherland
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,After me! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight! Fight, fight, fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about unlikely alliances... {no clue what he means: even so, woman?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll be going now, Mama. {likely not her real mom but the hostess, hence mama}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, we heard that someone\Nis stirring things up in the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Which gang are we fightin' this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The local army garrison.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Army...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, if that's a joke, it's a rotten one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This battle is not a joke. In fact,\NI am in part responsible for it happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll fight them to the death, if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,T-To death?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my duty to protect those two's happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, with that cleared up, \Nmove out of my way, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't sit back and watch after seeing your determination!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll defend whoever's happiness,\Neven if the world considers us just parasites. {/worthless people}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never did anything \Nfor the good of the world or others before!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow us this once-in-a-lifetime chance \Nto be useful to someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll back you up in any way we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll back you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, is that to say \Nyou're entrusting your lives to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, once again, this wedding \Nbecame the stuff dreams are made of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for me to go there \Nand defend Lady Benio to the best of my abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for you, I'll be sure to leave a big bump on Innen's forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough, just let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:53.83,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H020A26&\3c&H8AB5D0&\fs40\move(1534,135,340,135,500,4300)}Bring Sublieutenant home {少尉を返}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why are you all standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Count!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd all like to join your cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Before all else, \NBenio shares our blood. {/the same blood flows in her veins as in ours}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just stand here and watch idly \Nas she risks her life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But remember—we're going up against \Nthe Empire of Japan itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aware of that.\NI already went to my wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Go there and show them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...and had my farewell cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And we are on Lady Benio's side because
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we also oppose Young Master \Nbeing transferred far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:40.78,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H020A26&\3c&H8AB5D0&\fs80\pos(710,74)}Bring the lieutenant home!{少尉を返せ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you forbid us, \Nwe'll take matters into our own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two! One, two! One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.39,0:16:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait!\NAre you seriously gonna leave without me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the warlord in this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back! Ah... {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.91,0:17:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking to you, can't you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you expect me to react to your "Hey, you!"\Nwhen I was already in a bad enough mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But even putting that aside, I've just about had enough of men who wear sabers! {says\Nspecifically "guys who hang saber" for some reason, not own/have/wield/brandish but hang}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, easy now, no need to get so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I stopped you because of your dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're aware that rabies \Nhas been on the rise lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You did vaccinate these dogs \Nagainst rabies, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you did, you must have the certificate.\NI'd like to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case you must follow me to headquarters now \Nand get them properly vaccinated!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! I've no time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you, without that vaccine, \Nthey might get rabies at any moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be too late to act when that happens.\NPrevention is the best medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What about tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Folk always promise to get it done tomorrow \Nand run off, but never actually do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't complain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? Civil disobedience?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out! I told you to let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:19.69,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H211E25&\3c&H4F6976&\bord1}Imperial Army 1st Division HQ {帝國陸軍第一師団}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring the men out already! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:43.88,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H102234&\fs70\3c&HDDE6E6&\bord0\blur1\frz5.532\pos(434.4,304.8)}I want a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done vaccinating your dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You really didn't have to throw me into the cell \Nfor something this trivial!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.89,0:20:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say you got off lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.07,0:20:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at what you've done to us with your naginata and those dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio sure is taking her time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't suppose she's made a detour \Nto eat anmitsu or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, just as all these people are waiting for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Here she is! Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you, Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unfair, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, why did you all gather here today?\NAre we on some kind of strike?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, we've all come here to aid you \Nin your storming of the headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura, you have the worst grades \Namong my many students.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That said, your courage in telling off those selfish military men as a frail girl is nothing short of admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,On one hand, having a student such as you\Nhas brought me nothing but indescribable grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but, on the other hand, \Nit is also an indescribable honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.98,0:21:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's storm this joint together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight! Fight! Fight! Fight! Fight! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:20.20,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Teacher, everyone else... Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You've made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All these people came here for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.19,0:21:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't accept it—my opponent is the Imperial Army \Nand I can't drag anyone down with me. {/expose to danger}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Up until now, I've only ever acted \Nout of selfishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.99,0:21:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So please forgive me this one last selfish act!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only go there by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.25,0:21:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's for Shinobu, \NI'm prepared to die as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.09,0:21:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.37,0:22:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.44,0:22:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.95,0:22:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a certain day of a certain month of the year 1918,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.57,0:22:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and our traditional woman Benio is about to storm a garrison all by herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.31,0:22:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Although this event was never written \Nin any history book or official document...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.90,0:22:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But to set the record straight: \Nour High Collar Lady really did that, all on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going in and confronting Innen face to face!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.37,0:22:55.90,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(537.21,131.56)\bord0}In the next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.34,0:22:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There goes the High Collar Benio,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.32,0:23:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,forcing her way through worthless guards and demanding the despicable Lt Col Innen to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the danger High Collar Lady presents to his life,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.31,0:23:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt Col Innen is desperate and even attempts to flee.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,1st Division HQ is in total chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.70,0:23:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,See in the next episode of \N{\i1}Here Comes the High Collar Lady{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.90,0:23:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't Go, Shinobu!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.03,0:23:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:41.57,Default,,0,0,20,,Please call me High Collar Lady, \Nbecause I'm in that phase
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:48.49,Default,,0,0,20,,When it's getting so hard \Nto be honest with the people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:57.31,Default,,0,0,20,,I just want to know what's in his heart;\N I want him to turn around before he leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,20,,to give me that loving glance once again{made up to better match song pacing}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:05.69,Default,,0,0,20,,Ah, how frustrating it is \Nto have these unrequited feelings{/This unfulfilled wish is heavy}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:10.64,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.15,0:24:16.83,Default,,0,0,20,,Just a tomboyish lady who's a little pretentious
